data_filter¶

In [8]:
def data_filter(df):
  df.drop(['Alley','PoolQC','Fence','MiscFeature'],axis=True,inplace=True)
#numerical_cols
  if df.LotFrontage.isnull().any():
    df['LotFrontage'].fillna(method='ffill',inplace=True)
  if df.MasVnrArea.isnull().any():
    df['MasVnrArea'].fillna(value=0.0,inplace=True)
  if df.GarageYrBlt.isnull().any():
    df['GarageYrBlt'].fillna(method='ffill',inplace=True)
#obj_cols
  if df.MasVnrType.isnull().any():
    df['MasVnrType'].fillna(method='ffill',inplace=True)
  if df.BsmtQual.isnull().any():
    df['BsmtQual'].fillna(method='ffill',inplace=True)
  if df.BsmtCond.isnull().any():
    df['BsmtCond'].fillna(value='TA',inplace=True)
  if df.BsmtExposure.isnull().any():
    df['BsmtExposure'].fillna(value='No',inplace=True)
  if df.BsmtFinType1.isnull().any():
    df['BsmtFinType1'].fillna(value='Unf',inplace=True)
  if df.BsmtFinType2.isnull().any():
    df['BsmtFinType2'].fillna(value='Unf',inplace=True)
  if df.Electrical.isnull().any():
    df['Electrical'].fillna(value='SBrkr',inplace=True)
  
  if df.FireplaceQu.isnull().any():
    df['FireplaceQu'].iloc[0] = 'Gd'
    df['FireplaceQu'].fillna(method='ffill',inplace=True)
  if df.GarageType.isnull().any():
    df['GarageType'].fillna(method='ffill',inplace=True)
  if df.GarageFinish.isnull().any():
    df['GarageFinish'].fillna(method='ffill',inplace=True)
  if df.GarageQual.isnull().any():
    df['GarageQual'].fillna(value='TA',inplace=True)
  if df.GarageCond.isnull().any():
    df['GarageCond'].fillna(value='TA',inplace=True)


  if df.MSZoning.isnull().any():
    df['MSZoning'].fillna(value='RL',inplace=True)
  if df.Utilities.isnull().any():
    df['Utilities'].fillna(value='AllPub',inplace=True)
  if df.Exterior1st.isnull().any():
    df['Exterior1st'].fillna(value='VinylSd',inplace=True)
  if df.Exterior2nd.isnull().any():
    df['Exterior2nd'].fillna(value='VinylSd',inplace=True)

def infochart(df,feature_,chart=True):
  print('Unique values :',df[feature_].unique())
  print('Total nan     :',df[feature_].isnull().sum())
  print('Value counts  :\n',df[feature_].value_counts())
  if chart:
    plt.figure(figsize=(5,5))
    sns.displot(df[feature_],kde=False)

Feature Engg.¶

def Ordinal_en(df): maplist=[] for obj in object_cols : obj1={'col':obj,'mapping':{}} id=0 for value in df[obj].unique(): obj1['mapping'][value]=id id+=1 maplist.append(obj1)

ordinal_encoder = OrdinalEncoder(mapping=maplist) df=ordinal_encoder.fit_transform(df) return df

df=Ordinal_en(df)

In [35]:
def OneHot_en(df):
  for obj in object_cols :
    df_Dummies = pd.get_dummies(df[obj],prefix=obj,prefix_sep='_',drop_first=False)
    for var in df_Dummies.columns:
      df[var] = df_Dummies[var]  
  df.drop(object_cols,axis=True,inplace=True)
  return df
